==Spanish==

===Phrase===
'''[[buscar]] [[pelo]]s en la [[sopa]]'''

# to look for [[excuse]]s to [[complain]]; literally "to search for hair in the soup"

[[Category:Spanish phrases]]

===Examples===
* ¿Por qué buscabas pelos en la sopa? - Why did you look for excuses to complain?
* Siempre buscas pelos en la sopa. - You always look for excuses to complain.